flowRoot.flowPara: Variety: In 2017 there were 3,396 unique journals, 28,293 unique keywords and 104,985 authors.
Variety: As the literature expands, so does its complexity, with more active authors, specialised journals and niche topics.
Veracity: A rapidly declining proportion of the literature is captured in IPCC reports, heightening the risk of selective referencing

text.tspan: The 3 V's of the big literature on climate change
